li.span: ESP32 loops through all 11 ATtiny addresses sequentially
Builds a frame for each ATtiny containing its specific LED status string
Transmits each frame over RS-485 to all ATtinys
Each ATtiny listens to every frame but only accepts frames matching its own address

li.span: ESP32 updates seat booking data from Supabase every ~10 seconds
After each fetch, new LED strings are parsed and updated
Each ATtiny receives new data continuously in a loop
If data fetch or parsing fails, LEDs retain the last known state
